subject: Tennis
Deaths (Obituaries)
Fashion and Apparel
lead_paragraph: Ms. Moran, who made it as high as No. 4 in the United States rankings, showed up at Wimbledon in 1949 wearing an unconventional short skirt with lace-trimmed underwear.
